campaign'' in the West to encourage citizens to leave East Germany.
Tass said the campaign and ``propaganda hullabaloo'' were conducted
to pressure East Germany.
   East Germany ``is an inalienable part of the Warsaw Treaty, is
our true friend and ally,'' Tass said.
